em from an obsessive campaign of terror. Many of the Stalker’s victims die from exhaustion or simply surrender after years of pursuit. Beware should it take an interest in you. Wherever you go, it follows." },            new("Spawn The Trickster", "spawnboss_boss_trickster_normal") { Category = "Spawn Boss", Description = "A Reaper that specializes in murder by illusion. Treasure hunters especially fall foul of the Trickster’s deadly jokes, eagerly pocketing the gems it manifests and learning all too late that they’ve stuffed their pantaloons with supernatural explosives. Loves to be the death of the party." },            new("Spawn Tri-Anchors", "spawnboss_boss_dragogion") { Category = "Spawn Boss", Description = "Its father was a great beast that arrived to this world within the belly of a meteor. Its mother was a fish. Each head has its own personality, core values, and political affiliation." },            new("Spawn Trickster (Xl)", "spawnboss_boss_xltrickster") { Category = "Spawn Boss" },            new("Spawn Trinacria", "spawnboss_boss_trinacria") { Category = "Spawn Boss" },            new("Spawn Triton (Xl)", "spawnboss_boss_xltriton") { Category = "Spawn Boss" },            new("Spawn Werewolf", "spawnboss_boss_werewolf") { Category = "Spawn Boss" },            new("Spawn Werewolf 2", "spawnboss_boss_werewolf2") { Category = "Spawn Boss" },            new("Spawn Witch 2", "spawnboss_boss_witch2") { Category = "Spawn Boss" },


